There are so many things that has happened...that i dont even know where to start. 
   First i am so happy cause it's a new year, and i have a great new job in my career... of massage therapy..
 I finally finished school and i am a free woman...until i go back to school next fall...
Second, I have learned so many things about the challenages in life and why it comes to you...and it has changed me alot.  I believe that i am a different person...not completely different but somewhat different...
I have lost a great deal in my life this past year....and it all started from june but...now i know things that i wish i could explain what happened but i would rather not say....it's kind of embrassesing(i dont know if spelled that right, i have a brain fart, lol) but lets just say that i wish i could keeps some things that i have lost and change the past, in some way, but then that wouldnt make me the person that i am today....:) and i am pretty happy about it...
lets just say that right now...many things are changing and i am happy(for that most part any way.)

There are so many things that are going to be happening soon in my life: Such as being finished with school. In med june I will be finished with school and hopefully with god good will i will pass the final test.  Then i can go and get my state license for Massage Therapy.  
Then what do i do? Do i move back home? All i have ever own to do is work and school.  and with school out of the way and done with i'm gong to be going into the real world and do my career (if so be it).  I have been thinking about these questions for about 3 months now. And i have yet to come up with an answer. Now that its getting closer to the finsih line and am starting to lose sleep, and im not eating right like i use to anyway. I need an answer(advice) and nobody will give me one. I feel like all lost and confused.  and i dont know what to do

Well, as the title as i got a NEW JOB!!! It has to do with phones, and setting up appointments. I'm not a telemarketer. I just call you and tell you about something free!!! May be its not the thing i want to do right now but the only reason is for CAsh!! for my new apartment with my new roommate, who doesnt have a job anymore. reason: because idk...they told her something then they changed they're minds or something like that. well anyways, ive got to get back.

There are so many things that has happened to me since the last time, that i almost saw the light!!!

Recently i have moved once more...(its not the last time)with my co-worker Maria.  Welll the reason is because my cousin decided to pick-up and go without telling anyone in the family. But the thing is that since she didnt well we were basically all out of town (she is a coward). I mean, come on her mom(my aunt)was out of the country. I was out of the city along with 6 other members of my family and the others where basically out of the state.  I leave for five days and call her be4 i leave to go home to tell her what time i going to be getting there. and she just comes out and says "I LEFT" i came to live with my (bummpy,oilly,chineselooking,noballs)(my words not hersin my mind)boyfriend.  and says ill talk to you later.bye.

what kind o f bullshit is that. i mean she did exactly what she said she wasnt going to do. which was:

leave with out tellling

leave her apartment lease

and leave without telling you're MOTHER!!!

so i'm left out in the streets. basically. well thats what it felt like.

so i tell my co-worker this and she says i can stay with her until october when her lease is up.

I couldnt believe what I did the other day. I was going back home from school. And i am at a red light. So i look at my sterring wheel and think and think about just things in my life that are happening. and I sweer at the corner of my eye i saw the light turn GREEn.  So my foot automatically  stepped on the gas and went for it. and then theres a truck that just went right in front of me. and i stopped and i looked at the light and i couldnt believe it. the light was still red and i was in the middle of the street.  I could almost had a heart attack. and then there was a semi-truck coming my  way so i just went for it. and went i crossed completely. i looked around to see if there was any cop around and ooo my goosh i was amazed. There wasnt one in sight.  but i am still scared because you know they are ssend a ticket and mail it to your home. so yeah i am still scared because of that.
then afterwards i call my boyfriend you tell him about it. and he didnt even ask if i was okay. he was just yelling at me the hole time i talking to him. But thats okay. because thats all i can do...is yell because he cant do anything to me at all.

know what to talk about something interesting but i dont know what?
     Well, lets talk about two of my friends they are lesbos (Cindy and Karen).  And they

want to get marriend and have the happy lovely gay family.  Like having kids and well

On the day of the superbowl,alex's mom came up to me and said that she had to talk to me. so i said ok. well, she started off by saying that she wasn't going to leave afterall.(I knew in my gut that, that was going to happen) and i looked at her with such anger because then she started to say that she didnt know what i wanted to do. if i wanted to move out at the end of the month. or go live with a friend where. and some other shit like that. basically she was kicking me out. and looked. then she said that oo im not kicking you out im just telling you. may be we could all move into a house or someshit. then she said okay. and turned around and left. so i called my mom and told her what this fuck'n bitch said. she got mad then decided to come to phx,az and we decided tom move in with my cousin for a while and here i am. at mycousin i dont have to pay rent or anything but ill help to be fare. ehhe but just a little. hehe i have to save.!!!

Yesterday, I was having a pretty good day. Until I work where I see my phone and I notice that i have a couple of missed calls. And i notice that they are from my roommate Alex. She left my a message saying that to call her back as soon as possible that it is very important.So okay, im thinking like what the hell. so i called her big ass back and she starts to, to tell me about cashing my rent check that she went twice and that i didn't have enough money in for it and all this other shit about,

"This is not going to be happening and all of this other shit."

and it sounded like as if i was the child and she was the fuck'n mother!!! And that just pissed me off really bad. so whatever i finished work and went to my friends house for an hour or two. then i went home and she wasn't there and i waited and waited for like 15 minutes and 15 minutes is like forever when your mad. So i finally tired to go to sleep and it took me and Hour. until that happened. and i haven't seen her today. but when i get home she is going to hear me and i am going to be so mad. and she wont hear the end of it.  hehe

Satuarday when i was going to work i was on the freeway. And there was an amber alert on the electronic signs. (an amber alert=is when a child has been kiddnapped) so anyways, i didn't know what an amber alert was. So i called my mother, and she told me. I got to work late but it was okay because my boss wasn't there yet, either, so i wasn't in trouble.   they told me all about every detail because it would come up on the radio like every 10 minutes. 

Well at work it was really boring no one that i actually like talking to was there, and all the people that i really didnt like was there.   I went home and no one was there which was great because i like to be by myself for a little while but not all dam night and day.  I locked both doors because i thought my roommate and her mother was out of town.  and like about 1:30am my roommate calls me telling me that she couldnt open the door. so i was going down stairs and then she opens it all by herself. 

Early in the morning i wake up and my roommate wasn't there and enither her mother. Which was also great but kind of weird. I did nothing at all most of that day sunday until 1:30pm. i went to the swap met but i couldn't find it.  So i just went to walmart instead and i was going crazy because of babies were yelling and screaming at the top of their lungs. Well i bought lots and lots of food for myself.  like 3 different orange juices and i big ass apple juice.  (by the way i love juice) and i came home and still no one was there) and now i was just starting to worry but they came home later on at night.

I need money cause 1st of all i am way way way... behind on my bills and i dont like that at all, but yet who does.  second, some more bills are coming up and i'm going to get more behind on my bills. what is a girl to do?? besides going to the corner. hehe j/k
my boyfriend tells me to stop worrying that it will get done when it gets done but i worry thats my thing.

How many people in LJ actually take this dam thing seriouly??  Me, you could say that sometimes i take it serious and sometimes i dont.  I think it all depends on in what mood your in...  the person who post on their journal then the other poeple who actually read it.  For example, you could take my boyfriend nick.  I think that he does take the journal serious at times but just doesnt admit it. but for me I do sometimes but not all the times. sometimes i may act like it but i dont because why would people write all their personal things that they actually feel for tons of people could read!??

Lately, its been so busy for me that i barely talk 2 my boyfriend these days!!! I've been getting up going to school. then going home-cleaning my room which always ends up in a mess anyways. then i go to work or just go to the gym with my cousin. And she pushes me because she really wants me to lose all this dam weight i've gained!!! That my family keeps on telling me that i get bigger everytime i go visit. and i'm TIRED of hearing the samething. you need to lose weight laura. go do something excercise. and now i am but i'm just so tired of everything. and now i've been putting in applications in a couple of places and i've gone to a couple of interview in the last couple of days, and its funny because everything is going good like i'm completly qualified for the job, but then it going downhill from there. And i think i'm started to get homesick because i haven't gone since Christmas and thats every rare for me. I was going to go this weekend but this morning i got a call from work say that something happened to the Samatha ( the girl that was working for me) and now i have to do it. So i dont know when i'm going to be going over. and i really starting to miss my boyfriend much more then i usually do. and i'm tired of everything and i just want to leave and hide.

I'm so excitied, i'm going home this weekend. for three days. and hopefully.  i get to go and visit my family in mexicali, cause i have gone since like more then a month.  and the last time i went, everyone was happy to see me because i hadn't gone since like may or some shit!!  well, hopefully ill get 2 go c everyone i havent seen in a long time.  ooo and i'm going 2 go pick up my friend Veronica from her boyfriends house. so she can come back to phoenix. i'm happy cause she went 2 flordia, disney world, universal, and some other parks that i want 2 go c. i going 2 c her after like 3 weeks that she has been gone. im happy!!

now my roommate that i got into a fight with. told his girlfriend (lis) that he wants to talk to me but cant because i dont know!!! yeah thats the bullshit that he told her. well, anyways, i still dont talk 2 him because he needs to apologize to me because of that. so i could be in the kitchen and he wont even say hi or anything. but thats okay cuz my mommy says that LIFES A BITCH, AND YOU CAN BE ONE TOO BUT MORE OF A BITCH!!! he also told her that he wants me to go and talk to him. but i dont think so. i'd rather sell myself on the fuckn street then doing that shit!!!lol well anyways enought about that shit:

My roommate was accusing me of stealing his fuck'n remote. and so he thought i took it so he took my fuck'n CD's. so we get into it about why the fuck was it in between my stuff. and all this other shit. and i'm like i dont know and thats its not my fault about how you loose yourself. and he's like okay you get my shit and i'll get yours. i'm like fine then its going 2 b this way then fine FUCK YOU!!! There is no possible way i am going 2 4give him unless he say's he's SORRY!!! i am very pissted off and i am sure i am going 2 move out. but the thing that really gets me is that i know my roommate liz ( his girlfriend) didnt believe me. so im like fuck it then... and other thing that really pissed me off was that he came into my dam room and YELLED @ me. i mean that is some real BULLSHIT!! there.

what the fuck is the bullshit about asking your roommate if they have the rent when you dont even have it yourself???  i mean what the fuck is that all about?  that is what my roommate did to me yesterday.  he asked me if i could give him the money for the rent and then he'll pay it off on friday when it was dur wednesday.  No i told him that i was going to go pay it myself because i would feel better that way if i would do it.  i dont TRUST him. so today i went and talked to the fuck'n apt. manager about us not having the money. so she said that friday we had to have it in or she will charge us late fees.  so okay i get it.  whatever.  but my roommates are fuck'n lazy yeah thats right LAZY.  they say that they are going to do something.  but they dont do it. or they do it like an hour later.  Then today i went to the old apts. were i use to live at like 2 months ago.  and they said that i owe this much and my roommate owes that much and if you dont pay by this amount of time.  then this much money would be added.  then they said that they wanted this bullshit and that crap.  and its just all getting on my FUCK'N nerves.  i mean WHAT THE FUCK IS THIS??? when i wanted to get off the lease they said no because the people staying would have to approve and have all this money.  and now they still dont have all this money but they want us off the lease by this time of day.. and then when i go the fuck'n and dam bitchy lady has this fuck'n attitude with me like im STUPID or some shit.  treating me like a dam child and no it doesnt work that way.  i mean i'm a adult so they call it!!! at 18 right!!??  people are going to hear me today!!!!

As you guys know many people go out for the holiday. you know they go and see their family.  and all of that stuff but not me and my room mates we didnt do anything. because i had to work like a dumbass standing there waiting for freak'n people to come and see me like always.  but okay some people did come but they got on my dam nerves because some of them kept on asking the same questions at the same time. then they just wouldnt shut the F up.  i mean you can understand the same people coming over and over and then asking the same dam thing again and again. so i ignored them because i didnt give a dam.  well anyways i didnt get to go w/ my familia because of that and then the next day i had to wait 4 my cuz 2 get off of work for we can leave. well then after my cuz got off i had 2  wait 4 her boyfriend 2 get off too.  okay. but we finally got home and i got 2 c my boyfriend. i was happy.  but i would have gotten home earlier if it wasnt for these dam peoples.  some people need 2 get there own rides home and stuff.  but im not realy b_ch'n about it cuz i got chinese food and a nice shirt out of it.  so im happy about that. and i got 2 go 2 a mall i have never been too.  so theres another outcome. i guess. well neways theres some of my holiday happiness. but there is no cheer for me.  other then i went home and saw all of my family. and that i saw my boyfriend. who ate all of my COOKIES!!

last night we were all having fun but then me and my friend vero had to go to sleep.  becuz of school.  and the everyone else left to the jacuzzy.  but i think that crazy cuz its cold.  but anyways finally me and vero went 2 sleep and it was just me and her in the house.  and then all of a sudden the door to the other room was slammed closed.  and then the funny thing was that there was no wind and no one else was home but me and her.  so i told her thats funny. theres no wind and its just me ad you here.  so we got scared. and then we heared to more doors close.  and then we heared the guys come in. and we got up and told them and they were scared too.  because they told us all kinds of scarey things stuff has been happening.
